column2: "...good work. Once again, I think those were good moves. They're ideal for a Force."
"...I understand why everyone's talking about you. When I see your abilities, I want to talk to someone about them."
"...that was a bit of a tangent. Here is your reward for this. Thanks for going with me."
"...that's all for now. See you. I'll be looking forward to having another chance to work with you."
